control of the c-file, the bishops are strong, there is a pin on the weak
e6-pawn, so overall, Black has a tough defense ahead.}) (10... Bg4 11. Qa4 $16
{[%csl Rd5][%cal Gf1d1]}) 11. Rc1 Bg4 {Black is trying to provoke h3. White
