leads to an advantage.} (7. cxd5 $5 {Capturing on d5 also makes some sense as
well since Black doesn't want to recapture with the pawn.} Nxd5 (7... Qxd5 8.
Bf4 O-O 9. Nbd2 $14 {White wants to continue with Nb3 and then recapture the
