Nc6 {The most played move and best try from Black.} (7... dxc4 8. Qa4+ $1 Qd7 (
8... Nbd7 9. Qxc4 O-O 10. Nc3 $14 {White's light-squared bishop is much
stronger than the opponent's, so that gives White an advantage. The move Rd1
